            "title": "中國引導民營糧食企業響應全穀物行動計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國正指導民營糧食加工企業擴大和升級全穀物生產，這是加強糧食安全、實現農業供應鏈現代化的更廣泛舉措的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家糧食和物資儲備局周六發布的新聞稿引述局長劉煥鑫的話稱，國家「十五五」規劃綱要引領糧食產業發展方向，其中，實施全穀物行動計畫拓展糧油產品市場新空間。行動計畫旨在擴大營養豐富的穀物和油料產品供應，並提高加工效率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該倡議被視為中國長期戰略的一部分，旨在使食品消費與公共衛生目標保持一致，並減少加工和流通過程中的損失。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2ce4b7aa-f12f-36a7-bf9a-6778311546d2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">劉煥鑫表示，政府還強調糧食加工企業需升級技術並提升糧食流通效率。當局將完善與民營企業的常態化溝通機制，以更好地協調政策實施並解決運營中的問題。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Urges Private Grain Firms to Tap Whole‑Grain Policy Push</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:t